cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the design and implementation of an open-source machine learning library, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The library also includes algorithms for computer vision (cs.CV) and data science (cs.DS), and the emphasis on speed and flexibility suggests a focus on optimization and efficiency, which is also relevant to neural networks (cs.NE).
